	   <tr><td colspan=2>Level 60 ogre warrior here too try and shed some light on the hp issue for you guys,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;    First i have a unbuffed completely nekid hp of 2705 i think it might be 75 but i have a base stamina of 150 i think hp is modified by your base stamina thus an ogre warrior gets more hp per level and after level 30 there is a hp bonous not sure if just for warrior i think all malee,then at level 50 + there is another hp bonous for everyone.<br>       Too put it short when i got all the gear that id like too have someday i figured it out for me having 4510 hp on the dot...<br>        But as far as monk's worring about warriors i good monk friend of mine using his primal velium brawl stick beats the tar out of me on a regular basis 8x monks being second too rogue in damage out put makes up for there lack of stamina and hp . Have too take into account that the levels 1-50 warriors get Taunt Slam ( if big race) kick as skills thats all we get in those 50 levels slam being the only class specific skill but you have too also be race specific too get it with out the use of a shield.<br>(im talking about use able skills IE: Feign death mend wounds flying kick back stab)<br><br>Level 60 Warlord<br>Brell Serilis<br><br>PS: Btw trust me ogre's earn those extra hp  and ablity not too be stunned from frontal attacks Neg 15 % exp for kills kos too anything and to everything There are places we just cant fit unless shrunk which is a pain in the butt if you dont have any shaman friends around plus were generally big fat stupid and ugly and mostly not liked very well .But you wont here many complaints about us when were maintanking hehe.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
